com.esri.mo2.map.core
Interface NorthArrow

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseNorthArrow
public interface NorthArrow
extends Cloneable

NorthArrow interface defines a set of methods needed for a NorthArrow object. In addtion to the drawing methods, it mostly defines a set of getter/setter methods for the properties of a NorthArrow.
